<subSubSection pageId="1" pageNumber="294" type="diagnosis">
<paragraph blockId="1.[151,1437,1346,1731]" pageId="1" pageNumber="294">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[151,273,1346,1371]" inLineHeading="true" pageId="1" pageNumber="294" reason="1">Diagnosis.</emphasis>
Corallum monopodial and pinnulate. Pinnules in two lateral rows and in one or more anterior rows. Lateral pinnules simple or with a small ramified subpinnule; anterior pinnules short, generally not longer than 
<quantity metricMagnitude="-2" metricUnit="m" metricValue="1.0" pageId="1" pageNumber="294" unit="cm" value="1.0">1 cm</quantity>
, and subpinnulate. Polyps 
<quantity box="[487,602,1418,1443]" metricMagnitude="-3" metricUnit="m" metricValue="5.5" metricValueMax="6.0" metricValueMin="5.0" pageId="1" pageNumber="294" unit="mm" value="5.5" valueMax="6.0" valueMin="5.0">5 to 6 mm</quantity>
in transverse diameter.
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
<subSubSection pageId="1" pageNumber="294" type="discussion">
<paragraph blockId="1.[151,1437,1346,1731]" pageId="1" pageNumber="294">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[199,315,1454,1479]" inLineHeading="true" pageId="1" pageNumber="294" reason="1">Remarks.</emphasis>
The new species, described below, followed the original description by 
<bibRefCitation author="Opresko, D. M." box="[1153,1333,1454,1479]" pageId="1" pageNumber="294" pagination="129 - 165" refId="ref5028" refString="Opresko, D. M. (2005) New genera and species of antipatharian corals (Cnidaria: Anthozoa) from the North Pacific. Zoologische Mededelingen Leiden, 79, 129 - 165." type="journal article" year="2005">Opresko (2005)</bibRefCitation>
with the exception of some of the lateral pinnules presenting a ramified subpinnule similar to the anterior pinnules in all but its smaller size.
</paragraph>
<paragraph blockId="1.[151,1437,1346,1731]" pageId="1" pageNumber="294">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[199,628,1562,1587]" pageId="1" pageNumber="294">
Species assigned to 
<taxonomicName authorityName="Opresko" authorityYear="2011" box="[467,621,1562,1587]" class="Anthozoa" family="Cladopathidae" genus="Heteropathes" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Animalia" order="Antipatharia" pageId="1" pageNumber="294" phylum="Cnidaria" rank="genus">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[467,621,1562,1587]" italics="true" pageId="1" pageNumber="294">Heteropathes</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
.
</emphasis>
Included in the genus are 
<taxonomicName authority="Opresko (2003 b)" authorityName="Opresko" authorityYear="2003" box="[995,1385,1562,1587]" class="Anthozoa" family="Cladopathidae" genus="Heliopathes" kingdom="Animalia" order="Antipatharia" pageId="1" pageNumber="294" phylum="Cnidaria" rank="species" species="americana">
<emphasis box="[995,1161,1563,1586]" italics="true" pageId="1" pageNumber="294">H. americana</emphasis>
<bibRefCitation author="Opresko, D. M." box="[1180,1385,1562,1587]" pageId="1" pageNumber="294" pagination="275 - 280" refId="ref4993" refString="Opresko, D. M. (2003 b) A new species of Allopathes (Cnidaria: Antipatharia) from the eastern Atlantic. Zoologische Mededelingen Leiden, 345, 275 - 280." type="journal article" year="2003">Opresko (2003b)</bibRefCitation>
</taxonomicName>
, 
<taxonomicName authority="Cooper (1909)" authorityName="Cooper" authorityYear="1909" class="Anthozoa" family="Cladopathidae" genus="Heliopathes" kingdom="Animalia" order="Antipatharia" pageId="1" pageNumber="294" phylum="Cnidaria" rank="species" species="heterorhodzos">
<emphasis italics="true" pageId="1" pageNumber="294">H. heterorhodzos</emphasis>
<bibRefCitation author="Cooper, C. F." box="[316,482,1598,1623]" pageId="1" pageNumber="294" pagination="301 - 323" refId="ref4419" refString="Cooper, C. F. (1909) Antipatharia. Reports of the Percy Sladen Trust Expedition to the Indian Ocean. Transactions of the Linnean Society, London, Series 2 (Zoology), 12, 301 - 323." type="journal article" year="1909">Cooper (1909)</bibRefCitation>
</taxonomicName>
, and 
<taxonomicName authority="Opresko (2005)" authorityName="Opresko" authorityYear="2005" box="[542,853,1598,1623]" class="Anthozoa" family="Cladopathidae" genus="Heliopathes" kingdom="Animalia" order="Antipatharia" pageId="1" pageNumber="294" phylum="Cnidaria" rank="species" species="pacifica">
<emphasis box="[542,667,1598,1623]" italics="true" pageId="1" pageNumber="294">H. pacifica</emphasis>
<bibRefCitation author="Opresko, D. M." box="[673,853,1598,1623]" pageId="1" pageNumber="294" pagination="129 - 165" refId="ref5028" refString="Opresko, D. M. (2005) New genera and species of antipatharian corals (Cnidaria: Anthozoa) from the North Pacific. Zoologische Mededelingen Leiden, 79, 129 - 165." type="journal article" year="2005">Opresko (2005)</bibRefCitation>
</taxonomicName>
.
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
